extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Johnson's Local Library], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts, which dynamically update as you add authors, genres, books, and bookinstances or copies of books (see links in the navigation bar on the left-hand side of the page):

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.book_instance_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.book_instance_available_count}
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}